---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Nate Cowperthwaite"
  description="Chef turned self-taught developer. I build small tools to solve real problems — not for hire, just for fun."
  side="dev"
>
  <main>

    <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
    <section class="about-hero hero-gradient-bg">
      <div class="orb-container" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="orb orb-blue"></div>
        <div class="orb orb-indigo"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero-inner">
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">👤 About Me</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="about-hero-title animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.07s">
          Chef by trade.<br />
          <span class="shimmer-text">Builder by habit.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="about-hero-sub animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.14s">
          I've spent 10+ years in professional kitchens — from line cook to sous chef.
          Somewhere along the way I started building tools to fix the friction I kept running into.
          That became a genuine obsession. I'm not looking for a job or clients.
          I just like making things that actually work.
        </p>
        <p class="about-hero-back animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.20s">
          <a href="/dev" class="inline-link">&larr; Back to Dev Home</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== WHO I AM ===== -->
    <section class="section section-blue-tint">
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Who I Am</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">The short version.</p>

      <div class="who-grid stagger">

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon">🔪</div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Still a Chef</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            Full-time kitchen work is still my day job. I've led BOH teams, written menus,
            managed food cost, and done the hard unglamorous stuff that keeps a kitchen alive.
            Dev is what I do when service ends.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon">🛠️</div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Self-Taught Dev</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            No bootcamp, no CS degree. I learned by building things I actually needed — recipe tools,
            kitchen ops automation, AI-assisted workflows. If something bugs me enough I'll figure out
            how to fix it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon">🧪</div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Driven by Real Problems</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            Every project here started with a genuine irritation — something slow, something missing,
            something that should exist but doesn't. I'm not building for a portfolio.
            I'm building because I needed it to exist.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon">🤖</div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Deep in AI/Agentic Workflows</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            MCP, AI APIs, agentic tooling — I work with this stuff daily. Not as a trend chaser,
            but because it's actually useful when you point it at a real workflow
            instead of a demo.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-animated"></div>

    <!-- ===== WHAT I BUILD ===== -->
    <section class="section section-blue-wash">
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">What I Build</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">Small tools. Real use cases. No roadmaps.</p>

      <div class="build-list stagger">

        <div class="build-item reveal">
          <span class="build-dot">▸</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Kitchen & food ops tools</strong> — recipe scaling, cost tracking,
            prep management. Stuff chefs actually need and can't afford at enterprise pricing.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="build-item reveal">
          <span class="build-dot">▸</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Automation for repetitive workflows</strong> — if I'm doing the same thing
            more than twice I'm building something to handle it.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="build-item reveal">
          <span class="build-dot">▸</span>
          <div>
            <strong>AI integrations that are actually useful</strong> — not chatbots for the sake of it,
            but agents that slot into a real task and make it faster.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="build-item reveal">
          <span class="build-dot">▸</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Whatever I'm annoyed by this week</strong> — the best projects start with
            "why doesn't this exist yet."
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-animated"></div>

    <!-- ===== CONTACT ===== -->
    <section class="section section-blue-tint">
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Say Hi</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">
        Not hiring, not for hire. But if something here is interesting to you — I'm around.
      </p>

      <div class="contact-grid stagger">

        <!-- Email -->
        <a
          href="mailto:shadowwalkernc@gmail.com"
          class="contact-card card card-glow-blue reveal"
          aria-label="Send an email to Nate"
        >
          <div class="contact-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">✉️</div>
          <div class="contact-card-body">
            <div class="contact-card-label">Email</div>
            <div class="contact-card-value">shadowwalkernc@gmail.com</div>
            <p class="contact-card-note">
              Best for anything that needs an actual conversation — feedback, ideas,
              collaboration on a weird side project. I try to reply within a couple days.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-card-cta">Send a message &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <!-- GitHub -->
        <a
          href="https://github.com/ShadowWalkerNC"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="contact-card card card-glow-blue reveal"
          aria-label="View Nate's GitHub profile"
        >
          <div class="contact-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🐱</div>
          <div class="contact-card-body">
            <div class="contact-card-label">GitHub</div>
            <div class="contact-card-value">ShadowWalkerNC</div>
            <p class="contact-card-note">
              Everything I'm building lives here. Open issues, leave feedback, or
              just poke around. Pull requests on anything public are welcome.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-card-cta">View profile &rarr;</div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ---- Section tints ---- */
.section-blue-tint {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg,
    rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.04) 0%,
    transparent 100%);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
}
.section-blue-wash {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg,
    rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06) 0%,
    rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.03) 100%);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.10);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.10);
}

/* ---- Hero ---- */
.about-hero {
  position: relative;
  padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.18);
}
.about-hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg,
    rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.07) 0%,
    transparent 60%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.about-hero-inner {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0;
}
.about-hero-inner .badge { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.about-hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.about-hero-sub {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.75;
  max-width: 560px;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.about-hero-back { font-size: 0.88rem; }

/* ---- Who I Am grid ---- */
.who-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.25rem;
}
.who-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
}
.card-blue-left {
  border-left: 3px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.30);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg,
    rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05) 0%,
    var(--bg-elevated) 60%);
}
.card-blue-left:hover { border-left-color: var(--accent-blue); }
.who-card-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; line-height: 1; }
.who-card-title {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin: 0;
}
.who-card-text {
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin: 0;
}

/* ---- What I Build list ---- */
.build-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  max-width: 680px;
}
.build-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
  font-size: 0.93rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.10);
  transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
}
.build-item:hover {
  border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25);
  background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.07);
}
.build-item strong { color: var(--text-primary); }
.build-dot {
  color: var(--accent-blue);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  margin-top: 0.28rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ---- Contact cards ---- */
.contact-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.25rem;
  max-width: 720px;
}
.contact-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  padding: 2rem 1.75rem 1.5rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-left: 3px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg,
    rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.04) 0%,
    var(--bg-elevated) 50%);
  transition: transform 0.22s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1),
              box-shadow 0.22s ease,
              border-color 0.22s ease;
}
.contact-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  border-left-color: var(--accent-blue);
}
.contact-card-icon {
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  line-height: 1;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.20));
}
.contact-card-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; flex: 1; }
.contact-card-label {
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.6);
}
.contact-card-value {
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--accent-blue);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.contact-card-note {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}
.contact-card-cta {
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--accent-blue);
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateX(-6px);
  transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}
.contact-card:hover .contact-card-cta {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateX(0);
}

/* ---- Responsive ---- */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .about-hero   { padding: 3.5rem 1rem 2.5rem; }
  .who-grid     { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
